      {
         "id": "SECTION_conclusion",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Conclusion</h3>On this page, we learned how to create larger numbers, but we limited ourselves to representing numbers that can be associated with our fingers. These numbers have names without a well-defined pattern. On the next pages, we will learn about the connection of numbers with our families.</p>",
               "source": null,
